    Reviewed-by: Ren√© J.V. Bertin <rjvbertin@gmail.com>
    Reviewed-by: Alex Blasche <alexander.blasche@qt.io>
    Reviewed-by: Oswald Buddenhagen <oswald.buddenhagen@qt.io>

